{"tid":931470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美10歲女童欺凌同學　被父罰2°C走8公里上學","createTime":"2018-12-07T05:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T14:09:22.000Z","uid":75969,"like":923,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"dd44f1cd6eaef83be1d1b1ead9c15e5e91194a21","tid":931470,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T05:13:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181207/s00005/43bfc8a5ae7cb756c0f9424b1e567b2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181207%2Fs00005%2F43bfc8a5ae7cb756c0f9424b1e567b2e.jpg&h=2aa97cd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國俄亥俄州一名父親為了懲罰女兒欺凌同學，要她在攝氏2度的天氣下，步行8公里上學，父親的做法在網上引發熱議。<br />\n<br />\n10歲女孩克絲汀（Kirsten）因第二次欺凌同學，被學校禁乘校車3日。克絲汀回家告知父親考克斯（Matt Cox）此事，並說要父親開車載她回校。考克斯知道後，決定教訓女兒，命她徒步上學。<br />\n<br />\n周一（3日）克絲汀在攝氏2度的天氣下，步行8公里上學，而考克斯就駕車尾隨女兒，並拍下過程。他在片中說：「我知道很多家長不同意我這樣做，這沒關係，我正在做我認為正確的事去教導女兒，並阻止她欺凌別人。」<br />\n<br />\n懲罰克絲汀的影片在facebook已有接近1800萬觀看次數及7.3萬個回應。有網民的自閉症孫兒曾遭欺凌，看到考克斯的影片後留言：「我為你鼓掌！太多父母什麼都不做」；但也有網民反對考克斯的做法，認為他是欺凌女兒：「將懲罰她的影片上載到facebook來羞辱她，諷刺。」<br />\n<br />\n片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/matt.cox.735/videos/2191578667575986/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmatt.cox.735%2Fvideos%2F2191578667575986%2F&d=KSHrbrcZAjs90lyxCGdwewCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=a6f385ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/matt.cox.735/videos/2191578667575986/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20181207/s00005/1544152811324/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20181207%2Fs00005%2F1544152811324%2F&d=KSHrbrcZAjs90lyxCGdwewCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f09cc572\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20181207%2Fs00005%2F1544152811324%2F&h=6fecae30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20181207/s00005/1544152811324/</a><br />\n<br />\n之前都好似有一單差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過係男童"},{"pid":"db352363803572676b10dfeda657e61e281f9d72","tid":931470,"uid":41818,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T05:14:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647cb9ff26c09f0c76a57b7d767bdf005fdf6c17","tid":931470,"uid":113626,"like":532,"dislike":5,"score":527,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T05:15:15.000Z","msg":"香港既話會blame the victim<br />\n要求被欺凌者自行退學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分分鐘玩埋metoo"},{"pid":"b65e0ba7a6945f1a5d5c2a8367c66482ce1b2a37","tid":931470,"uid":53705,"like":288,"dislike":12,"score":276,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"如果是支那人, 一定會讚自己個女做得好, 以後要繼續欺凌更多人"},{"pid":"07adabf5edef1000f1ce459662ed7ca4fe0ba74d","tid":931470,"uid":46527,"like":473,"dislike":1,"score":472,"quote":{"pid":"b65e0ba7a6945f1a5d5c2a8367c66482ce1b2a37","tid":931470,"uid":53705,"like":288,"dislike":12,"score":276,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"如果是支那人, 一定會讚自己個女做得好, 以後要繼續欺凌更多人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T05:16:30.000Z","msg":"她只是個孩子啊"},{"pid":"a3b0635ba5234fce25401fbdfca99b67214228e2","tid":931470,"uid":191926,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T05:16:30.000Z","msg":"做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a347b59eb2a0e4f4947a1594bf343c53ce908a","tid":931470,"uid":42487,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"quote":{"pid":"b65e0ba7a6945f1a5d5c2a8367c66482ce1b2a37","tid":931470,"uid":53705,"like":288,"dislike":12,"score":276,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"如果是支那人, 一定會讚自己個女做得好, 以後要繼續欺凌更多人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T05:16:39.000Z","msg":"他只是個孩子.jpg"},{"pid":"5e4900738b9fa343c683a297058d6bf2b08eceb5","tid":931470,"uid":63870,"like":292,"dislike":2,"score":290,"citedBy":0,"r